comments: Replay review of the foul called on Powell (POR) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful, but the foul on the floor is changed from a shooting foul to a non-shooting foul.
Nurkic (POR) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Mitchell (SAC) and makes marginal contact to the back but does not affect Mitchell's ability to defend.
Nurkic (POR) avoids making contact to the arm and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt from Mitchell (SAC).
Fox (SAC) moves laterally into McCollum's (POR) body and affects his SQBR during the driving shot attempt.
Nurkic (POR) dislodges Mitchell (SAC) from his position during the rebound.
Fox (SAC) makes contact with Powell (POR) body that affects his play at the basket.
Lillard (POR) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).

Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact as he has a resting arm that collapses on the lower body of McCollum (POR) as he gathers and enters his shooting motion. The contact does not affect McCollum's ability to make the shot.
While pursuing the loose ball, McCollum's (POR) hand makes contact with the baseline out of bounds while he is touching the ball.
Nurkic (POR) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
